and global VP, I developed and executed a strategic vision, leveraging AWS, IBM, Rackspace, SAVVIS and CSC partnerships to expand Racemi, Inc.'s Global Reach, achieving 80%+ sales growth year-over-year. Today, as a seasoned Amazon business development strategist, I continue to build and lead high-performing global teams to generate $5 Billion in revenue by 2030, establishing actionable, transformational strategies, delivering a clear, and compelling vision to align and drive for overall productivity and success. I bring to bear a unique blend of Global Business Perspective, Strategic Planning and Execution, Team Building \\u0026 Leadership, Think Big Partnership Development and operational excellence. I am passionate about driving transformative change while fostering a culture of trust and team empowerment to achieve extraordinary results.\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1e:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L19\\\",\\\"Advisor\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-serif text-2xl text-[color:var(--color-indigo)] mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-[color:var(--color-border-gold)]\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Advisors\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",\\\"1b6MyJ1Eqm2TlUQBDgmUKe\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"relative group flex gap-5 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-6 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[#52B788]/30 transition-all duration-300\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"shrink-0 h-16 w-16 rounded-full p-0.5 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#52B788] to-[#1A3A2E] self-start mt-0.5\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"relative h-full w-full rounded-full overflow-hidden bg-[#1A3A2E] flex items-center justify-center text-white text-lg font-serif\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L1a\\\",null,{\\\"src\\\":\\\"https://images.ctfassets.ne