 equity deals. Known affectionately as the \\\"Fairy Godmother\\\" to the founders she mentors, Samina's mission is clear: accelerating humanity's evolution to cure chronic illness and extend healthy lifespans. She is a sought-after keynote speaker on longevity, biohacking, and the convergence of science, spirituality, and technology — having spoken at events like the Biohacker Summit , where she shared her personal protocols for reversing biological aging. Samina's impact extends beyond business — she has served on steering committees for the Perez Art Museum Miami and the Dream In Green Gala, reflecting her commitment to community and purposeful living.\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1f:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L19\\\",\\\"Industry Expert\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-serif text-2xl text-[color:var(--color-indigo)] mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-[color:var(--color-border-gold)]\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Industry Experts\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",\\\"4mJogdOqhQvsb28LML8Iq\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"relative group flex gap-5 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-6 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[#52B788]/30 transition-all duration-300\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"shrink-0 h-16 w-16 rounded-full p-0.5 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#52B788] to-[#1A3A2E] self-start mt-0.5\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"relative h-full w-full rounded-full overflow-hidden bg-[#1A3A2E] flex items-center justify-center text-white text-lg font-serif\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L1a\\\",null,{\\\"src\\\":\\\"https://images.ctfassets.net/lp5y22r82q1h/6hddhyJTcaX3ONlW0V30SN/2bb3a8aa84c9d62a49bafa7e34dba0df/78B1C98A-C232-4CEF-B944-33BBA7AD92B5.avif\\\",\\\"alt\\\":\\\"Profile photo of Samina Rind\\\",\\\"fill