ess. I bring to bear a unique blend of Global Business Perspective, Strategic Planning and Execution, Team Building & Leadership, Think Big Partnership Development and operational excellence. I am passionate about driving transformative change while fostering a culture of trust and team empowerment to achieve extraordinary results.8:[\"$\",\"$L2\",\"Advisor\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"font-serif text-2xl text-[color:var(--color-indigo)] mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-[color:var(--color-border-gold)]\",\"children\":\"Advisors\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",\"1b6MyJ1Eqm2TlUQBDgmUKe\",{\"className\":\"relative group flex gap-5 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-6 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[#52B788]/30 transition-all duration-300\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"shrink-0 h-16 w-16 rounded-full p-0.5 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#52B788] to-[#1A3A2E] self-start mt-0.5\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"relative h-full w-full rounded-full overflow-hidden bg-[#1A3A2E] flex items-center justify-center text-white text-lg font-serif\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L3\",null,{\"src\":\"https://images.ctfassets.net/lp5y22r82q1h/7AqiOx1rAdlZWeRJBUFUl8/109566124b1ce403ad389e0a5360ff8b/1768844958127.jpeg\",\"alt\":\"Profile photo of Lorraine Bassett MBA, PHD\",\"fill\":true,\"sizes\":\"64px\",\"className\":\"object-cover\"}]}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"min-w-0 flex-1\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-semibold text-[#1A3A2E] group-hover:text-[#2D6A4F] transition-colors\",\"children\":\"Lorraine Bassett MBA, PHD\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[#52B788] text-sm font-medium mb-2\",\"children\":\"Impact Advisor\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[#0F1A14]/60 text-sm leading-relaxed line-clamp-2 mb-3\",\"children\":\"$e\"}],\"$Lf\"]}],\"$L10\"]}],\"$L11\",\"$L12\"]}]]}]\n13:T6a3,Samina Rind is a visionary entrepreneur, investor, keynote speaker, and longevity ambassador based in Miami Beach, Florida. A Princeton University alumna and University of Cambridge graduate, Samina brings over 20 years of experience across business development, strategic partnerships, fundraising, and venture investing. What makes Samina's story remarkable is her personal transformation. After surviving a brain tumor larger than a golf ball while scaling her first startup, she embarked on a 14-year journey of rigorous health optimization at the intersection of science, technology, and spirituality — achieving a biological age in her early 20s at the calendar age of 53. Today, Samina serves as Founder, CEO, and General Partner of #highminded ventures , where she advises and invests in pioneering health, longevity, and biotech companies. She is an advisor and investor to companies like KÄÄPÄ Biotech and Maya Health , and a Limited Partner and Advisor at Catalyst Holdings , co-investing in lower-to-middle market private equity deals. Known affectionately as the \"Fairy Godmother\" to the founders she mentors, Samina's mission is clear: accelerating humanity's evolution to cure chronic illness and extend healthy lifespans. She is a sought-after keynote speaker on longevity, biohacking, and the convergence of science, spirituality, and technology — having spoken at events like the Biohacker Summit , where she shared her personal protocols for reversing biological aging. Samina's impact extends beyond business — she has served on steering committees for the Perez Art Museum Miami and the Dream In Green Gala, reflecting her commitment to community and purposeful living.9:[\"$\",\"$L2\",\"Industry Expert\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"font-serif text-2xl text-[color:var(--color-indigo)] mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-[color:var(--color-border-gold)]\",\"children\":\"Industry Experts\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"gr